.about-page
  .container
    hgroup
      h1 Welcome to BOOZ
      p Inventory management and cocktail creation for home bars and cocktail enthusiasts.


    .sections-grid
      .grid-item.explanation

        section.explanation-section
          h2 Why BOOZ?
          p I've tried other bar inventory apps, but they were either too complex for my needs or lacked the features I wanted. I built BOOZ to be simple, intuitive, and tailored to the needs of home bartenders.

        section.features
          h2 Features
          ul
            li Manage all the bottles in your bar with detailed information
            li Keep track of the beer and wine in your fridge
            li Manage essentials like bitters, syrups, and garnishes
            li Suggest cocktails based on what you have available
            li Easily create shopping lists to restock your bar
            li Create and share your own custom cocktails.
            li Let your guessts know what's available right now with the "Available Now" feature and QR code menu.
      
      section.grid-item.admin-screens
        h2 Behind The Scenes
        p Some screenshots of the bar management.
        .admin-screens
          //- Each anchor keeps a normal href for non-JS fallback, but opens modal when JS available
          button.full-link(type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" data-full="/images/screenshots/admin/full-1.webp" data-alt="BOOZ admin interface — inventory management" @click.prevent="openModalFromEvent($event)")
            img(src="/images/screenshots/admin/thumb-1.webp" alt="BOOZ admin interface — inventory management")
          button.full-link(type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" data-full="/images/screenshots/admin/full-2.webp" data-alt="BOOZ admin interface — cocktail creation editor" @click.prevent="openModalFromEvent($event)")
            img(src="/images/screenshots/admin/thumb-2.webp" alt="BOOZ admin interface — cocktail creation editor")
          button.full-link(type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" data-full="/images/screenshots/admin/full-3.webp" data-alt="BOOZ admin interface — bottle details and tags" @click.prevent="openModalFromEvent($event)")
            img(src="/images/screenshots/admin/thumb-3.webp" alt="BOOZ admin interface — bottle details and tags")
          button.full-link(type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" data-full="/images/screenshots/admin/full-4.webp" data-alt="BOOZ admin interface — availability and QR menu" @click.prevent="openModalFromEvent($event)")
            img(src="/images/screenshots/admin/thumb-4.webp" alt="BOOZ admin interface — availability and QR menu")

      .grid-item.demos
        section.demo-links
          h2 Try The Demo

          p Want to see BOOZ in action? Check out the demo bars below to get a feel for how it works and what it can do for your home bar.

          .demo-link-wrapper
            NuxtLink.demo-link(:to="'/sample'") 
              h3 Sample Bar
              p A modest collection of bottles, a few beers and wines, and some basic essentials. It's a great starting point to see how BOOZ works and to get a feel for the features.

            NuxtLink.demo-link(:to="'/lemon'")
              h3 Lemonhaus
              p We're not afraid to show what this looks like in production. Lemon keeps his bar inventory updated with BOOZ, and you can see how he uses it to manage his home bar.

      .grid-item.next-steps
        section.contact
          h2 Open Your Own Bar
          p Ready to manage your bar's inventory and cocktails? Contact Lemon to set up your own BOOZ account. It's probably cheaper and easier than you're expecting.
